snippet: Li Haotong, 20, of China, was in contention at the HSBC Champions, a World Golf Championships event in Shanghai, after a six-under-par 66 in the third round left him one shot out of the lead.
abstract: Li Haotong shoots six-under-par 66 to trail by one shot in third round at HSBC Champions; other golf scores noted.
